description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a new challenge and want to be a part of our amazing team? We are currently recruiting &lt;strong&gt;Cleaning/Catering Assistants&lt;/strong&gt; to help us keep our hospital clean, and our patients fed. &lt;strong&gt;With a new hourly rate of £9.21 per hour on weekdays, £9.21 41% for weekday nights (after 8pm) &amp; Saturdays, and £9.21 + 83% for Sundays and Bank Holidays, there isn&#39;t a better time to join the team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Cleaning and Catering Assistant, you will be helping to support the clinical team in their delivery of a high standard of patient service and clinical care to the people of our local population.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be responsible for maintaining a safe, clean &amp; hygienic environment, whilst providing a catering service to our inpatients. Your main responsibilities will be to clean the hospital to the required standard following NHS cleaning protocols; you will lead in the cleaning of clinical and non-clinical areas. You will also be responsible for the serving of food to our patients, providing a basic catering service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are currently recruiting for staff to work the following shift patterns:-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Mon - Fri - 07:00 - 14:00 - 32.5 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Sat - Sun - 13.30 - 20.00 - 12 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Mon - Thurs - Week 1- 12:00 - 20:00 - Week 2 - 15:00 - 20:00 - 25 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- 5 days over 7 relief - working between 7am to 10pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We currently only have this availability so please only apply if you can work one of these shift patterns.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We also offer great benefits which include:-&lt;/strong&gt;• Starting salary of £9.21 per hour!&lt;br /&gt;• This post also attracts pay uplift for unsociable hours if worked.&lt;br /&gt;• 27 days holiday per year pro rata&lt;br /&gt;• Paid statutory holidays&lt;br /&gt;• Contributory pension scheme&lt;br /&gt;• Flexible working hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
